## Decomposition Guardrails
- Target: 6–8 epics per project overview (hard cap 10). If >10, consolidate by shared KPI/persona/workflow overlap.
- This is NOT an epic if it is a single workflow step (e.g., "Search", "Login", "Export CSV") or a single subsystem. Demote those to Features.
- Platform/foundation work must be outcome-framed and bundled (max 1–2 platform epics). Do NOT create separate epics for CI/CD, logging, metrics, auth unless the scope is truly cross-cutting and outcome-owned.
- Each epic MUST specify at least one measurable Success Metric (KPI or proxy + measurement plan). If baseline is unknown, state how it will be measured.
- Feature budget guidance: target 2–4 Features per Epic (hard cap 5).

