## Decomposition Guardrails
- Target: 2–4 Features per Epic (hard cap 5). If you have more, merge overlapping features by shared user workflow and shared data entities.
- This is NOT a Feature if it is <=5 days for one dev; demote to a PBI.
- Promote to an Epic if it requires >=2 teams or spans multiple distinct user workflows/personas.
- Avoid splitting by UI pages; split by user workflow stages and observable outcomes.
- Keep Features capability-framed ("Users can…"), not implementation-framed ("Implement…").

